<header class="doc-header">
  <div class="label">Design System Reference · v3</div>
  <h1>Cara A. Brown, MBA — <strong>Visual Identity</strong></h1>
  <p class="sub">caraabrown.com · Elementor + WordPress · EB Garamond + Outfit · Updated 2025</p>
</header>

<nav class="doc-nav">
  <a href="#color">01 · Color</a>
